IT'S EITHER GOT SOME REALLY
BAD GAS IN IT

14:40.896 --> 14:42.241
OR A COUPLE OF DEAD PLUGS.

14:42.241 --> 14:43.655
Mike:
TONY'S GOT BAD GAS.

14:43.655 --> 14:45.689
Tony:
THAT WAS YESTERDAY.

14:45.689 --> 14:47.896
SO THIS IS WHAT'S SUPER COOL.
MY 'CUDA JUST GOT HERE.

14:47.896 --> 14:51.000
THESE GUYS HAVEN'T SEEN IT YET,
BUT SUPER RAD, SUBLIME GREEN,

14:51.000 --> 14:52.413
BUT IT'S GOT ALL THE NEW BELLS
AND WHISTLES,

14:52.413 --> 14:54.034
YOU KNOW, MODERN MOTOR,
MODERN TRANS,

14:54.034 --> 14:56.689
FOUR-WHEEL BRAKES,
COILOVER SUSPENSION,

14:56.689 --> 14:59.965
BEAUTIFUL PAINT AND BODY, AND I
STOLE IT FOR ONLY 45 GRAND.

14:59.965 --> 15:02.137
WHAT DO Y'ALL THINK OF THAT?

15:02.137 --> 15:04.137
-WHAT PART OF THAT?
-IT'S PRETTY DECENT.

15:04.137 --> 15:05.517
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, MAN?

15:05.517 --> 15:07.862
IT'S ALSO GOT A 5-SPEED IN IT
INSTEAD OF A 4-SPEED.

15:07.862 --> 15:09.379
-YEAH, NO, THAT'S...
-YEAH, THAT'S COOL.

15:09.379 --> 15:11.310
I STOLE THIS CAR
FOR ONLY 45 GRAND.

15:11.310 --> 15:14.310
HEY, I FEEL BETTER ABOUT WHAT
WE KNOW THAN IF HE STOLE IT.

15:14.310 --> 15:15.931
WAIT.
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THEY THINK

15:15.931 --> 15:17.551
THEY KNOW,
BUT HERE'S WHAT I KNOW,

15:17.551 --> 15:20.551
THAT YOU AT HOME NEED TO KNOW
ABOUT HOW I GOT THIS '70 'CUDA.

15:23.344 --> 15:24.896
I WAS IN FLORIDA
CHECKING OUT A SHOP

15:24.896 --> 15:27.068
I INVESTED IN FOR MY SHOW,
"GARAGE REHAB."

15:27.068 --> 15:28.586
YOU'VE PROBABLY SEEN IT.

15:28.586 --> 15:30.448
ANYWAYS, I WAS TAKING CARE OF
BUSINESS WITH CHRIS AND RUSSELL.

15:30.448 --> 15:32.482
BECAUSE THEN THEY HAVE
THE AUDIO WORK THAT THEY DO.

15:32.482 --> 15:34.344
THEY HAVE ALL THE AIR
SUSPENSION THEY DO,

15:34.344 --> 15:36.000
SO EACH ONE CAN HAVE
A DESIGNATED AREA

15:36.000 --> 15:37.896
WITH THE SPECIALTY EQUIPMENT
AS NEEDED.

15:37.896 --> 15:39.586
WHAT'S THAT?
IS IT YOURS?

15:39.586 --> 15:40.862
NO, IT AIN'T MINE.

15:40.862 --> 15:42.034
LOOKS LIKE SOMETHING
YOU'D OWN.

15:42.034 --> 15:43.344
LOOKS LIKE
SOMETHING YOU DID.

15:43.344 --> 15:45.620
-YO!
-YES, SIR?

15:45.620 --> 15:47.103
WHERE THE [BLEEP]
IS MARK DICKS?

15:47.103 --> 15:48.965
APPARENTLY, THIS GUY HAD LEFT
HIS MOTORCYCLE

15:48.965 --> 15:50.310
AT THE SHOP TO BE REPAIRED.

15:50.310 --> 15:52.206
AFTER I CALMED HIM DOWN,
I WANTED TO FIND OUT

15:52.206 --> 15:53.551
ABOUT SOMETHING
THAT CAUGHT MY EYE.

15:53.551 --> 15:55.137
WHAT'S THAT?
THAT'S MY 'CUDA.

15:55.137 --> 15:57.517
HEY, Y'ALL GET TO WORK.

15:57.517 --> 16:00.137
NOW, I LOVE BARRACUDAS,
ESPECIALLY IF THEY'RE GREEN.

16:00.137 --> 16:02.482
THESE CARS ARE HOT RIGHT NOW,
AND THOSE CRAZY MOPAR COLLECTORS

16:02.482 --> 16:05.068
